## ✅ PR SUBMISSION CHECKLIST (Every single PR)

```
[ ] Branch name follows convention (fix/, feat/, docs/, refactor/)
[ ] Sync with upstream main before creating branch
[ ] Changes match EXACTLY what the issue asks for
[ ] All existing tests pass: python -m pytest test/ -v
[ ] Linting clean: flake8 on changed files
[ ] Commit message uses conventional format
[ ] PR title matches commit message
[ ] PR body references "Closes #XXXX" or "Fixes #XXXX"
[ ] PR body explains WHAT, WHY, and HOW TESTED
[ ] No unrelated changes included
[ ] No debug prints or commented-out code
```
